Adding one vegetable to this combination often gets you to 60. Be very careful adding more than three components (protein, grain, vegetable) as this frequently leads to 'overcomplicated' items with negative values. 'Water' seems to worsen already bad items, so avoid it on complex dishes. When you hit 60, it's often best to submit to avoid negative values.
